# Latest Update Manifest

This file is used by the Tauri auto-update system to notify users of new updates.

**Setup:**
1. Sign your release builds with `cargo tauri signer`
2. Upload signed installers to your release server
3. Update this file with new version information
4. Host this file at the URL configured in `src-tauri/tauri.conf.json`

---

